* manage applications from a public repository(https://appimage.github.io/feed.json)
* only cmd
* auto create links after install apps and remove too
* allow install applications like this: appcenter install app from repository
* manage applications from a private repository
* install applications in a local directory (without root, such as mac)
* automatic update of applications
* synchronize installed applications using an online account
* allow you to administer scripts to install applications that are not in a repository